caption:
🐣🥞 This morning was our 𝗘𝗮𝘀𝘁𝗲𝗿 𝗕𝗿𝗲𝗮𝗸𝗳𝗮𝘀𝘁 here at Anago, and what a great way to kick off the holiday weekend! 💐 

But we couldn’t let it pass without giving a special shoutout to our March Madness winners: congrats to Vaneska for snagging 1st place, Karen in 2nd, and Tammy in 3rd (even if she couldn’t be there)! And a big happy birthday to Raul – hope it’s a great one! 🎉

It’s always nice to step away from our desks, share a bite, and enjoy each other’s company, without discussing work. 😉 These moments remind us how important it is to pause, connect, and celebrate as a team. 💬☕️

Big thanks to everyone who helped put it together - and to our amazing team for making it so fun. Until the next one! 💙

#CompanyTraditions #EasterBreakfast #WorkCulture
